Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Christmas in Vermont, 1976
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w1bc
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 2 Jan 1977
Enjoying the fruits of his family's labours at a traditional New England Christmas gathering. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less